snippet.title: Delhi Police Arrest a Thug with Rs 3.5 crore in Old Currency Notes

localized.description:
Delhi police arrested a thug with Rs 3.5 crore in old currency notes. This thug used to cheat businessmen and convert the old notes of Rs 500 and Rs 1000.
